{
  "name": "session-pilot",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "Live multi-repo worktree dashboard with Claude session indicators (LIVE/idle/none), one-click claude --resume launch into Zellij Web Client, multi-key shift+click sort, virtual-scrolled table, full-message modal, parallel JSONL scan with SWR cache. Pairs with Zellij Web Client (port 8082) on dashboard port 8083.",
